room_title: Escape room "Grandma's Ugly Sweater" by The Great Xscape Room in Virginia Beach
room_address: 2548 Virginia Beach Blvd Ste 106, Virginia Beach VA 23452
room_description: You show up at Grandma's house to pick her up for your family's annual Ugly Christmas Sweater Party. Upon arrival, you realize that she is nowhere ready. She has forgotten where her ugly sweater and her keys are. Help Grandma retrieve her keys and her ugly sweater and make it to the party on time!
